{
  "stem": "2735.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He says he's going, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I said, what do you mean you're going, too?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "He says for money I can get a paper.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "He shows up at the train and he goes.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we travel through destroyed-- everything in Russia was destroyed, the bridges, the trains.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were crossing a train from Kiev.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It used to be a huge bridge that went all through town.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a temporary something.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was shaking like anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were no lights because there were blackouts.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my sister was-- she was a military nurse.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "She was wearing a custom made-- she's very little.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So she had a custom made military coat, and the hat, the whole thing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So she gave me to wear it because I didn't have a coat.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So she gave me the coat and the whole thing to wear.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We were in a car, in a passenger's car, driving at night full with soldiers, and they all drunk.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And such a poison, anti-Semitic poison spits from their mouths all night.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "That the Jews are fighting the war.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Uzbekistan and [NON-ENGLISH], that they getting rich on this speculeering-- speculations.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I mean, I can't even repeat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mean, I was afraid.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I thought we should jump the train.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Jump in the water, because they'll kill us in the morning.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And they-- and they don't even know if I'm a girl, because I just look like them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And I have my hat.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "In the morning was-- when it got light, we had to go and get some food.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we stopped somewhere.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And like nothing, didn't say a bad word.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They asked me if they can do this with me, can do something else with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
